text: Eating house lack of ventilation and wall fan installed far away from seating are super hot and humid .. eating in house will be sweating. Takeaway will be better option

Great place to find local food except Malay food. The owners should do a Spring-cleaning and get a new fresh coat of paint. The kopi-o is good. It is really age and many dirt spots. Corridor roof leaks during heavy storm.
Love the vegetarian food and nice coffee!
The coffee is tasteless...it's like drinking coloured water!
